OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772447793
OL,3,CMan arrested over social media post
OL,4,Ccalling for Jewish businesses to be
OL,5,Ctargeted
OL,7,FA 44-year-old man has been arrested
OL,8,Fafter a social media post called for
OL,9,FJewish businesses to be "targeted with
OL,10,Fstink bombs".
OL,12,FThe post, which appeared to be a
OL,13,Fcomment in the Brighton and Hove
OL,14,FPalestine Solidarity Campaign online
OL,15,Fgroup, also suggested throwing "ripe
OL,16,Ffruit and eggs" at synagogues.
