PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772447793
OL,3,CMan arrested over social media post
OL,4,Ccalling for Jewish businesses to be
OL,5,Ctargeted
OL,7,FSussex Police said officers attended
OL,8,Fan address in Newhaven on Sunday
OL,9,Fafternoon after receiving reports of
OL,10,Fthreatening comments posted on social
OL,11,Fmedia.
OL,13,FThe man was arrested on suspicion of
OL,14,Ffour offences: sending offensive,
OL,15,Findecent, obscene, or menacing
OL,16,Fmessages; using threatening words to
OL,17,Fstir up religious hatred; making
OL,18,Fthreats to damage or destroy property;
OL,19,Fand possessing a class B drug.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
