FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772447793
OL,3,CMan arrested over social media post
OL,4,Ccalling for Jewish businesses to be
OL,5,Ctargeted
OL,7,FHe remained in custody as of Sunday
OL,8,Fevening, the force said.
OL,10,F"We acknowledge the deep distress and
OL,11,Fconcern that can be caused by
OL,12,Fthreatening, hateful and anti-Semitic
OL,13,Fmessages to members of the Jewish
OL,14,Fcommunity, and the wider public," Det
OL,15,FCh Supt Richard McDonagh said.
OL,17,F"Threats of any kind are completely
OL,18,Funacceptable, and anyone who seeks to
OL,19,Ftarget individuals within communities
OL,20,Fof any faith group can expect a robust
OL,21,Fresponse.
OL,26,@vD@aO]
